Steps for docker:-
create a folder and initialize the npm in the folder
It creates the package.json file, package-lock.json file.
install express js
create a server.js file in the node-app
Create a Dockerfile
build the docker image
check the images in the
open the browser and check

For create AWS ECR we:-
Login to account 
Search for ECR 
And create repo
And add the user access id to github